title: Two of Hollywood's brightest new stars team up for 'Thoroughbreds'
text:
Two of Hollywood's brightest new stars team up for 'Thoroughbreds'   01:55 
Anya Taylor-Joy and Olivia Cooke, two of Hollywood's brightest new stars, talk about 'Thoroughbreds', a story of friendship and murder. Rollo Ross reports.
